00:45:19,516 --> 00:45:20,573
文又不行，武也不行
You can't do anything

551
00:45:20,716 --> 00:45:22,011
整天紧着出来行
Just hang around

552
00:45:22,316 --> 00:45:23,873
说了你不是这种材料啦
You are not anything

553
00:45:24,015 --> 00:45:25,777
是，我不是这种材料
Yeah, I'm not anything

554
00:45:25,949 --> 00:45:27,279
我最适合去卖鱼旦
I can only sell fishballs

555
00:45:28,549 --> 00:45:30,447
好，你叫我卖我便去卖罗
You ask me to do that

556
00:45:31,149 --> 00:45:32,274
卖到有一天我受不了
If I can't stand anymore

557
00:45:32,449 --> 00:45:34,347
我放些山埃落去毒死他们吧
I'll put poison on the fishballs

558
00:45:38,215 --> 00:45:39,613
为你好吧，你知不知呀？
It's good for you. Do you understand?

559
00:45:57,549 --> 00:46:01,709
Hi，这么巧呀？
Hi, what a coincident!

560
00:46:01,949 --> 00:46:03,381
对呀，真巧！
Right! Really a coincident!

561
00:46:07,015 --> 00:46:07,981
你好吗？
How are you?

562
00:46:09,149 --> 00:46:17,480
好！…我结婚了
Fine! I have married!

563
00:46:24,783 --> 00:46:28,772
好事，你老公对你怎么样？
Good! Are your husband treating you good?

564
00:46:29,649 --> 00:46:30,807
不错！
Quite good!

565
00:46:36,382 --> 00:46:38,541
这么大的雨，也不知要等到什么时候
So heavy is the rain! Who knows hot long will I have to wait!

566
00:46:39,382 --> 00:46:41,348
我在等我老公来接我
I'm waiting for my husband!

567
00:46:44,416 --> 00:46:45,677
抽不抽烟呀？
Have a cigarette?

568
00:46:46,149 --> 00:46:47,410
我戒了！
I didn't smoke anymore!

569
00:47:01,015 --> 00:47:02,379
不是你的
It's not yours

570
00:47:06,815 --> 00:47:07,747
我走了！
I leave now!

571
00:47:16,282 --> 00:47:17,145
拜拜！
Goodbye!

572
00:47:27,449 --> 00:47:28,710
阿娥在吗？
Is Ah-ngor here?

573
00:47:28,882 --> 00:47:30,905
她不在，是谁找她呀？
She is not here. Who are you?

574
00:47:32,716 --> 00:47:34,739
不用了，谢谢！
It's alright. Thanks

575
00:49:09,516 --> 00:49:10,174
小姐！
Lady!

576
00:49:10,549 --> 00:49:11,446
什么事？
What's the matter?

577
00:49:11,648 --> 00:49:12,671
阿娥在吗？
Is Ah-ngor here?

578
00:49:12,882 --> 00:49:15,280
不清楚，她好像去了九龙还没回来
I'm not sure! She had went to Kowloon and still haven't returned

579
00:49:16,382 --> 00:49:16,745
去了九龙？！
To Kowloon?

580
00:49:16,782 --> 00:49:17,713
是呀！
Yes!

581
00:49:20,449 --> 00:49:21,176
谢谢！
Thank you

582
00:49:21,282 --> 00:49:22,213
不客气！
You're welcome

583
00:50:14,316 --> 00:50:15,441
几时来的？
When did you arrive?

584
00:50:17,316 --> 00:50:18,475
刚刚来的？
I just arrived

585
00:50:24,082 --> 00:50:25,446
你好像肥了些！
You look a bit fatter than before

586
00:50:28,648 --> 00:50:29,671
少少！
A little bit

587
00:50:30,516 --> 00:50:31,708
你也是！
So are you

588
00:50:33,149 --> 00:50:36,172
全靠他，他是我的医生
It's all because of him He's my doctor

589
00:50:42,149 --> 00:50:43,547
你今晚在这里过夜？！
Would you stay up here tonight?

590
00:50:44,782 --> 00:50:47,942
不…我现在要回去了
No... I'm going home now

591
00:50:56,682 --> 00:50:57,410
阿娥
Ah-ngor!

592
00:51:00,815 --> 00:51:05,043
我想告诉你，我找到那只杯啦！
I just wanted to you tell that I've found that glass

593
00:52:02,481 --> 00:52:03,448
张小姐CaII你
Miss Cheung called you just now

594
00:52:03,615 --> 00:52:04,911
她说她现在正赶去梅窝码头
She said that she was going to the pier of Silver-mine Bay

595
00:52:05,115 --> 00:52:06,637
叫你无论如何都要等她
and told you to wait for her anyway

596
00:54:11,548 --> 00:54:12,707
你可以先上去睡觉
You may go to sleep

597
00:54:12,882 --> 00:54:14,370
明天我再帮你Checkin
& I'll check in for you tomorrow

598
00:54:15,815 --> 00:54:16,712
好
OK!

599
00:54:35,982 --> 00:54:37,278
明早几点返工？
When do you go to work next morning?

600
00:54:37,682 --> 00:54:41,478
很早的，我煮早餐你吃好吗？
Very early! I'll make breakfast for you

601
00:54:42,648 --> 00:54:43,636
好
Good!

602
00:54:48,348 --> 00:54:49,939
你打算住多久？
How long will you live in here?

603
00:54:51,848 --> 00:54:52,973
无所谓
It depends!

604
00:55:10,282 --> 00:55:11,611
我先走了
I leave now

605
00:55:13,982 --> 00:55:15,107
我送你
I see you off

606
00:55:15,415 --> 00:55:17,381
不用了，很近呀
That's OK! It's near

607
00:55:19,648 --> 00:55:21,307
你今晚可以不回去吗？
Would you not go home tonight?

608
00:55:25,182 --> 00:55:26,704
为什么到现在才来找我？
Why do you not visit me until now?

609
00:55:31,281 --> 00:55:33,214
因为我自己知道自己的事
Because, I know myself clearly

610
00:55:34,748 --> 00:55:36,475
我不可以答应你些什么
I cannot promise you anything

611
00:55:39,848 --> 00:55:46,474
如果我不是挂着你，我不会进来找你
If I'm not missing you, I won't visit you today

612
00:55:49,015 --> 00:55:51,038
如果你再不来找我
If you don't visit me in these days

613
00:55:51,381 --> 00:55:53,211
我可能同那个医生结婚
I will probably marry that doctor

614
00:56:58,049 --> 00:57:01,276
鱼蛋佬，我要一元，要多点酱
Fish-ball guy, give me one dollar of fish-ball with more dressing

615
00:57:08,848 --> 00:57:13,076
摆呀，怎么不摆？多点酱嘛
Take it, why don't you take it? You've said you want more dressing!

616
00:57:13,448 --> 00:57:16,573
摆呀，不摆我会庆的
Take it or I'll get mad

617
00:57:20,348 --> 00:57:23,439
鱼蛋佬？！你妈的！
Fish-ball guy? Damn you!

618
00:57:25,049 --> 00:57:29,242
不是吧，乌蝇哥，怎么霉成这样？
It won't, Mr Fly! Why are you so poor?

619
00:57:29,448 --> 00:57:30,971
搞到摆鱼蛋档？！
You don't have to sell fish-ball, do you?

620
00:57:31,548 --> 00:57:34,571
阴功罗
Poor guy

621
00:57:35,481 --> 00:57:37,344
一定是你大佬指使你的
It must be your Big Brother who told you to do so

622
00:57:38,214 --> 00:57:40,339
你呀就不要跟他了
You should leave your Big Brother

623
00:57:40,448 --> 00:57:43,937
你看我的马，个个身光颈靓
Look at my followers, all dressed up!

624
00:57:44,082 --> 00:57:45,980
摆大哥电话，用得着做吗？
Taking wireless telephone, do you need that?

625
00:57:46,515 --> 00:57:48,640
你跟的那个大佬
You bastard! Your Big Brother sent you

626
00:57:48,815 --> 00:57:50,178
叫你站在街上卖鱼蛋
selling fish-ball in the street

627
00:57:50,381 --> 00:57:51,904
跟我不是更好
Working for me is better!

628
00:57:52,148 --> 00:57:53,444
走鬼呀！
Escape

629
00:57:57,648 --> 00:57:59,773
走什么走呢？你是古惑仔呀
Escape for what? You are a gangster!

630
00:57:59,915 --> 00:58:01,278
有这么多兄弟在这里，你怕差人？！
We have so crowd of gangsters here! It's no need to afraid!

631
00:58:01,448 --> 00:58:02,243
动他呀！
Beat him!

632
00:58:04,748 --> 00:58:07,441
不用怕，有什么事进去了也不用怕
Don't be afraid! You'll be alright even if you're in jail

633
00:58:07,582 --> 00:58:08,878
有人敢动你马上还手
Fight back at one if someone beat you

634
00:58:09,015 --> 00:58:10,106
不要影衰班兄弟
Don't make us lose faces

635
00:58:10,715 --> 00:58:12,340
你这衰人，你…
You bastard, you...

636
00:58:12,515 --> 00:58:14,743
不用这么紧张，没事的
Take it easy! It's OK!

637
00:58:14,882 --> 00:58:17,245
你又不是卖白粉，只是卖鱼蛋嘛
You are not selling drugs, just fish-ball

638
00:58:18,348 --> 00:58:19,109
看戏！
Something good to be seen

639
00:58:53,448 --> 00:58:54,345
打四万啦！
Beat him!

640
00:59:07,782 --> 00:59:10,270
他妈的，别走呀！
Hey, don't go you bastard

641
00:59:11,015 --> 00:59:12,241
还走？
Don't go!

642
00:59:13,848 --> 00:59:14,973
去死啦！
Go to hell, bastard!

643
00:59:30,848 --> 00:59:32,814
拖他过来！
Take him here

644
00:59:42,415 --> 00:59:43,711
饮完啦！
Finished drinking

645
00:59:46,582 --> 00:59:48,514
对了，两箱鸡翼你猜有多少只？
Right! How many chicken wings are there in two boxes

646
00:59:49,949 --> 00:59:51,539
二、三百只啦！
About two or three hundreds!

647
00:59:52,915 --> 00:59:54,540
二、三百只？！
Two or three hundreds?

648
00:59:59,548 --> 01:00:01,912
喂，你回去了记得告诉你老板
Hey, go back and tell your boss...

649
01:00:02,048 --> 01:00:06,276
以后不要再叫你一个人搬
not to send you to take thing

650
01:00:06,515 --> 01:00:07,811
这么重的东西
so heavy alone

651
01:00:07,949 --> 01:00:11,073
告诉他，一只鸡翼打一捶
Or else, I'll give him one fist for one wing in return

652
01:00:12,014 --> 01:00:12,946
神经病！
You are crazy

653
01:00:13,081 --> 01:00:14,069
我神经病？
I am crazy?

654
01:00:17,348 --> 01:00:19,075
是不是不想我帮你？
Do you want me to help you?

655
01:00:19,248 --> 01:00:21,737
无所谓，反正我都不打算做了
It's OK! Anyway, I will quit!

656
01:00:22,081 --> 01:00:26,673
不做，为什么？
Quit! Why?

657
01:00:28,315 --> 01:00:30,338
我想到九龙去找工做
I want to find a job in Kowloon

658
01:00:32,248 --> 01:00:34,874
好呀，方便我，搬到我家来呀
Good! It's doing me favour! You can live in my house!

659
01:00:36,715 --> 01:00:38,305
你不要讲第二次
Don't say the second time

660
01:00:39,081 --> 01:00:40,638
讲了第二次就收不回了
You can't deny it if you say it twice

661
01:00:42,381 --> 01:00:44,040
我不是讲笑的
I'm not kidding!

662
01:00:45,248 --> 01:00:47,009
我出了去就不会再回来
I go out and will never come back

663
01:00:58,548 --> 01:00:59,979
喂，你吃什么呀？
Hey, what do you want to eat?

664
01:01:09,181 --> 01:01:11,670
你告诉他，我会准时上竹馆找他
Tell him that I'll go to find him on time

665
01:01:12,181 --> 01:01:14,204
如果乌蝇少了一条毛，唯他是问
If Fly has anything wrong, he'll pay for it

666
01:01:14,448 --> 01:01:15,277
就这样啦
It's finished!

667
01:01:16,981 --> 01:01:18,004
什么事呀？
What's the matter?

668
01:01:18,648 --> 01:01:21,045
没什么，我现在要出去，乌蝇出了事
Nothing special! Fly has some problem and I'm going out now

669
01:01:21,248 --> 01:01:22,407
会不会有危险？！
Would it be dangerous?

670
01:01:22,615 --> 01:01:25,809
没事的，我今晚就回来放心
No, it'll be alright, I'll be back tonight

671
01:02:35,481 --> 01:02:37,413
土申叔，这么多人呀？
Uncle Kwan, so many people here?

672
01:02:37,582 --> 01:02:40,548
华仔，这件事是乌蝇不对
Ah-wah, it's Fly doing wrong in this case

673
01:02:40,748 --> 01:02:44,009
不过，大家是自己人，无谓搞大了
But, I don't want to make it big since we all know each other

674
01:02:44,481 --> 01:02:47,276
过去跟TOny讲几句好话吧！
Say something good to Tony & the case will be settled

675
01:02:57,415 --> 01:03:00,847
TOny，乌蝇就算有什么不对
Tony, no matter what did Fly do,

676
01:03:00,981 --> 01:03:02,413
我都会执行家法
I'll punish him according to my rules

677
01:03:03,081 --> 01:03:04,513
请你把我细佬交给我
So please give me back my brother

678
01:03:04,682 --> 01:03:08,079
细佬？！什么细佬呀？
Brother? What kind of brother?

679
01:03:08,248 --> 01:03:11,078
这个是细佬吗？你喜欢掩住你的细佬
Is this a brother? You like to protect your brother

680
01:03:11,248 --> 01:03:13,180
现在掩住他呀
now you are protecting him!

681
01:03:13,847 --> 01:03:17,644
同我玩花样？是好马就该掩住他
Making fun of me? You should protect him if he is good

682
01:03:17,814 --> 01:03:20,781
你掩住“劈”屎，你怎么做人大佬呀
Now you are just protecting a lump of shit How can you be a Big Brother?

683
01:03:20,948 --> 01:03:22,914
TOny，拿回个彩就算了
Tony, stop when you have some advantage

684
01:03:23,081 --> 01:03:23,910
无谓去得这么尽
Don't go too far

685
01:03:24,081 --> 01:03:27,479
坤叔，你省省吧，我是教识他做人
Uncle Kwan, save it for yourself! I'm teaching him to grow up

686
01:03:28,248 --> 01:03:30,441
他的马可以这样对我
His gangster can treat me like this

687
01:03:31,014 --> 01:03:32,980
将来你们还有地方立足吗？
Where can we stand in the future then?

688
01:03:33,782 --> 01:03:36,304
人呢，我一定会做
I'll release him surely!

689
01:03:36,548 --> 01:03:39,446
不过一定要我麻，我的要求好低
But I must be satisfied My requirement is low

690
01:03:39,615 --> 01:03:41,308
只要你讲一句我喜欢听的
Just say one sentence I like

691
01:03:41,515 --> 01:03:42,742
我就速速放人
I'll release him

692
01:03:48,548 --> 01:03:50,104
这句说话你喜不喜欢听？
Do you like to hear these words

693
01:03:50,148 --> 01:03:51,205
你要不要你弟弟？
Do you want your brother?

694
01:03:51,348 --> 01:03:52,211
华仔！
Ah-wah!

695
01:04:12,348 --> 01:04:13,870
大佬！
Big Brother

696
01:04:19,214 --> 01:04:20,407
你好！
Are you alright?

697
01:04:23,348 --> 01:04:24,405
能不能走？
Can you walk?

698
01:04:26,448 --> 01:04:27,641
能！
Yes, I can

699
01:04:37,682 --> 01:04:40,170
你的“靓”扶起他，叫呀！
Tell your follower to help him stand

700
01:04:40,648 --> 01:04:41,636
扶起他！
Help him stand

701
01:04:43,281 --> 01:04:46,611
不用，我自己起来！
No, I can stand by myself

702
01:05:15,914 --> 01:05:17,403
我自己走可以了
I can walk by myself

703
01:05:30,114 --> 01:05:31,171
不要过来
Don't get near to me

704
01:05:33,348 --> 01:05:34,211
大佬！大佬！
Big Brother! Big Brother!

705
01:05:43,747 --> 01:05:44,838
我告诉你们俩
I tell you two,

706
01:05:44,981 --> 01:05:46,947
这件事就算找天皇出来也没得拆
this case can't be settled even if you bring the highest King

707
01:06:00,181 --> 01:06:04,943
乌蝇，这件事情肯定还有下文
Fly, this case certainly won't end up this way

708
01:06:05,114 --> 01:06:06,102
这些钱你拿去
You take this money

709
01:06:06,415 --> 01:06:08,937
回调景岭要等事情淡了些才好出来
And go back to Til-gang Lin and wait for the case to fade out

710
01:06:09,114 --> 01:06:10,137
我不回去！
I won't go!

711
01:06:10,847 --> 01:06:11,438
我发过誓
I've made a vow

712
01:06:11,647 --> 01:06:13,943
我不发达就不回调景岭见我老妈
I won't go back to see my mother if I do not succeed

713
01:06:15,847 --> 01:06:18,938
好，我同你去大屿山
OK, I go to Lantau Island with you

714
01:06:20,481 --> 01:06:21,639
为什么你一定要我走呢？
Why do you drive me away so insistly?

715
01:06:21,781 --> 01:06:25,111
为什么？我不想明天你一出门口
Why? I don't want you to be killed tomorrow

716
01:06:25,348 --> 01:06:26,711
就被人斩开几碌
when you go out

717
01:06:27,847 --> 01:06:29,006
你明知道那只是癫狗
You know he is just a mad dog

718
01:06:29,181 --> 01:06:31,272
为什么你不听我的话，偏要去惹他
Why don't you listen to me not to provoke him?

719
01:06:31,481 --> 01:06:34,776
不是我惹他，是他先来惹我呀
It's him who provoked me, I didn't provoke him

720
01:06:34,948 --> 01:06:37,380
难道我不该玩他，现在我玩他不起吗
Don't you think I should just about it! I have the power to play, haven't I?

721
01:06:38,747 --> 01:06:40,145
你玩得起吗？！
Don't you have the power to play with him?

722
01:06:41,214 --> 01:06:44,146
你玩得起就不会被人打到像个猪头炳
If you have, you won't be beaten so heavily and have face swollen up

723
01:06:47,148 --> 01:06:49,943
是，我是被人打得像猪头炳
Yes, I was beaten to have face swollen

724
01:06:50,081 --> 01:06:52,343
你嫌我映衰你，就别理我好了
You are blaming me on losing you face, you can leave me alone

725
01:06:57,548 --> 01:07:02,537
是你自己说的，不要贪口爽呀
No one force you to speak this Don't speak it for fun

726
01:07:04,181 --> 01:07:05,840
我现在就不理你
I leave you alone now

727
01:07:06,114 --> 01:07:07,546
如果你明天出门口没事的话
If you are safe when you go out tomorrow

728
01:07:07,781 --> 01:07:09,111
我就替你挽鞋
I'll do anything for you

729
01:07:51,747 --> 01:07:54,009
我们一向都不知道明天会怎么样？
We all don't know what will happen tomorrow

730
01:07:54,914 --> 01:07:55,937
对不对？
Do you agree?

731
01:08:06,981 --> 01:08:07,810
去宵夜
Let's go eating out!

732
01:08:11,381 --> 01:08:12,312
走啦
Come along!

733
01:08:46,315 --> 01:08:47,144
打他
Beat him!

734
01:08:51,614 --> 01:08:54,103
乌蝇，我灭你，我灭死你呀！
Fly, I twist your face I twist you to death

735
01:08:57,048 --> 01:08:59,105
这次我还暗算不到你
I can plot against you this time, can't I?

736
01:09:00,348 --> 01:09:01,608
你不要打我大佬呀
