什么事呀？
What is going on?

923
01:29:26,080 --> 01:29:28,012
没有，我知你怕热
Nothing. I know you don't like feeling hot

924
01:29:28,246 --> 01:29:30,110
买了一部冷气给你
So I buy you a air conditioner

925
01:29:30,913 --> 01:29:34,242
我们下面装了，你留给自己用吧
We're installed it down there. This one just leave in to you

926
01:29:35,446 --> 01:29:38,174
我不上来了，你爸爸在
I don't come up. Your father is here

927
01:29:39,047 --> 01:29:41,410
那个是你老公，不是我爸爸
He's your husband, not my father

928
01:30:17,346 --> 01:30:18,972
你走到几时才安乐呀
When will you calm down and stop escaping?

929
01:30:19,846 --> 01:30:21,334
你出来找我做什么？
Why did you come out to see me?

930
01:30:22,513 --> 01:30:24,070
你不要理我好不好？
Why don't you leave me alone?

931
01:30:25,813 --> 01:30:29,041
我不理你？我不理你那个理你呀？
Who will care for you if I don't?

932
01:30:35,780 --> 01:30:38,245
不要以为做完这件事就好威了
Don't think that you'll be famous after this task

933
01:30:40,279 --> 01:30:46,008
对，你今天做完，个个就会说你够姜
Right, everybody will say you are brave this time when you do that

934
01:30:47,680 --> 01:30:49,839
下个礼拜，还有人知道你是那一个
But no one will remember you next week

935
01:30:51,080 --> 01:30:52,511
但是那又怎么样？
But what become of you then?

936
01:30:53,047 --> 01:30:55,171
再迟点就没有人认识你乌蝇啦
No one will know you later

937
01:31:07,580 --> 01:31:09,842
我也为阿公做了不少事
I've done many things for godfather also

938
01:31:12,580 --> 01:31:17,444
我十四岁，十四岁就拿安家费
I had received money for death when I was fourteen

939
01:31:20,713 --> 01:31:22,269
我威过好多人啦？
I was greater than a lot of people, right?

940
01:31:23,313 --> 01:31:26,245
那又怎么样？现在不也是这个样子
But look at me! I'm just an ordinary man now

941
01:31:26,580 --> 01:31:30,273
你威风，你总算威风过呀
Anyway, you were famous for sometime!

942
01:31:31,379 --> 01:31:34,607
我呢？我怎么样？
But what about me?

943
01:31:37,246 --> 01:31:40,474
没有人看得起我，你就开心啦
No one notice me and you are happy about that

944
01:31:40,980 --> 01:31:42,878
我样样都被人家看小
People look down upon everything of me

945
01:31:43,179 --> 01:31:45,975
他们还说我是你裤档里的一条狗
They even said that I was a dog beneath you ass

946
01:31:46,146 --> 01:31:47,442
你知不知道？
Do you know that?

947
01:31:51,179 --> 01:31:54,111
我乌蝇宁愿做一日英雄
I would rather be three-minute hero

948
01:31:54,313 --> 01:31:56,245
都不想做一世乌蝇
I don't want to be a fly for all my life

949
01:31:58,546 --> 01:32:01,239
你让我一手一脚的做一件事好不好？
Let me finish a great task on my own, would you?

950
01:32:01,913 --> 01:32:03,344
就这一次啦
Just for this time

951
01:32:17,913 --> 01:32:23,345
好，你是不是决定要去？
OK! Did you decide to go?

952
01:32:24,980 --> 01:32:26,741
如果你去我就陪你去
I'll go with you if you want to

953
01:32:27,913 --> 01:32:29,640
要是你被人射到了我都替你补飞
I'll take revenge for you if you are shoot down

954
01:32:29,813 --> 01:32:32,643
你不要对我这么好呀，行不行？
Don't treat me so good, would you?

955
01:32:36,780 --> 01:32:38,678
我还你不起的
I can't pay you back

956
01:32:40,279 --> 01:32:42,268
我不想跟你讲这么多话
I don't want to talk so much with you

957
01:32:42,413 --> 01:32:44,538
只要你说去，我就陪你去
Just say it, and I'll go with you

958
01:32:45,980 --> 01:32:49,969
如果你不去的话，一齐回大屿山
We'll go to Lantau Island if you say no

959
01:32:53,246 --> 01:32:55,212
以后的事，我会搞定
I'll settle anything following

960
01:33:02,413 --> 01:33:06,743
好！好！好！
OK! OK! OK!

961
01:33:06,947 --> 01:33:08,207
我跟你回去
I go back with you

962
01:33:24,079 --> 01:33:25,375
阿财，阿财，你不要看不起人
Ah-choi, Ah-choi

963
01:33:25,580 --> 01:33:27,068
怎么你残成这样？
Don't look down upon other

964
01:33:27,580 --> 01:33:29,944
快点同大佬打招呼了
He used to be great and famous but now he was finished

965
01:33:31,413 --> 01:33:34,971
不要这么独食，分一些给阿财啦
Don't be so stingily! Give something to Ah-cho
